'''鼻竇炎'''（Sinusitis）是描述發生於[[鼻竇|鼻竇]]的[[炎症|炎症]]。常見症狀包含濃厚鼻涕、鼻塞，以及臉部疼痛<ref name="Ros2015">{{cite journal|title=Clinical practice guideline (update): adult sinusitis executive summary.|last2=Piccirillo|first2=JF|date=April 2015|journal=Otolaryngology--head and neck surgery : official journal of American Academy of Otolaryngology-Head and Neck Surgery|issue=4|doi=10.1177/0194599815574247|volume=152|pages=598–609|pmid=25833927|last3=Chandrasekhar|first3=SS|last4=Brook|first4=I|last5=Ashok Kumar|first5=K|last6=Kramper|first6=M|last7=Orlandi|first7=RR|last8=Palmer|first8=JN|last9=Patel|first9=ZM|last1=Rosenfeld|first1=RM|last10=Peters|first10=A|last11=Walsh|first11=SA|last12=Corrigan|first12=MD}}</ref>。其他症狀包含[[發燒|發燒]]、[[頭痛|頭痛]]、嗅覺減退、喉嚨痛，以及咳嗽<ref name="CDC2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov/getsmart/antibiotic-use/URI/sinus-infection.html|title=Sinus Infection (Sinusitis)|accessdate=6 April 2015|date=September 30, 2013|website=cdc.gov|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407181505/http://www.cdc.gov/getsmart/antibiotic-use/URI/sinus-infection.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NIH2012Sym">{{cite web|url=https://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/symptoms.aspx|title=What Are the Symptoms of Sinusitis?|accessdate=6 April 2015|date=April 3, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405025147/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/symptoms.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-05}}</ref>。咳嗽會於夜間加劇。嚴重副作用較為罕見<ref name="NIH2012Sym" />。臨床上將病程4周以下的鼻竇炎稱作[[急性|急性]]鼻竇炎（Acute rhinosinutis，ARS），延續12周以上則稱為慢性鼻竇炎（Chronic rhinosinutis，CRS）<ref name="Ros2015" />。

鼻竇炎可能肇因於[[感染|感染]]、[[過敏|過敏]]、[[空氣污染|空氣汙染]]，或鼻腔構造問題。最常見的案例為[[病毒感染|病毒感染]]<ref name="CDC2013" />。如果症狀持續十天以上未改善，可能就會造成[[病原菌|病原菌]]孳生。[[哮喘|哮喘]]、[[囊腫性纖維化|囊腫性纖維化]]，及[[免疫缺陷|免疫缺失]]患者可能會有復發鼻竇炎的現象。如果沒有懷疑有其他可能併發症存在，一般來說不需使用[[影像学|X光照影]]。慢性鼻竇炎則建議以鼻鏡或[[電腦斷層|電腦斷層]]檢查<ref name="Ros2015" />。

洗手、禁菸，和增加免疫力能預防某些鼻竇炎發生<ref name="CDC2013" />。疼痛症狀則可以使用如[[萘普生|萘普生]]、[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]等[[镇痛药|鎮痛藥]]緩解，[[鼻沖洗|鼻沖洗]]也許能緩解某些症狀<ref name="Ros2015" /><ref name="King2015">{{cite journal|title=Saline nasal irrigation for acute upper respiratory tract infections.|last2=Mitchell|first2=B|date=20 April 2015|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006821.pub3|volume=4|pages=CD006821|pmid=25892369|last3=Williams|first3=CP|last4=Spurling|first4=GK|last1=King|first1=D}}</ref>。急性鼻竇炎一般進行僅{{tsl|en|watchful waiting|積極觀察|}}<ref name="Ros2015" />，若症狀持續7-10日，且持續惡化，則可施予[[抗细菌药|抗細菌藥]]介入<ref name="Ros2015" />。已使用抗細菌藥者，第一線輔佐藥物建議選用[[阿莫西林|阿莫西林]]或[[阿莫西林克拉維酸鉀|阿莫西林克拉維酸鉀]]。某些慢性病人或许可以借助執行手術来缓解。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/treatment.aspx|title=How Is Sinusitis Treated?|accessdate=6 April 2015|date=April 3, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405025201/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/treatment.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-05}}</ref>。

鼻竇炎為常見的症狀<ref name="Ros2015" />。在歐美，每年約有一至三成的人會發生<ref name="Ros2015" /><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=vT9YAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA687|title=Middleton's allergy : principles and practice.|date=2014|publisher=Elsevier Saunders|isbn=9780323085939|edition=Eight|location=Philadelphia|page=687|last1=Adkinson|first1=N. Franklin|access-date=2017-03-15|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603211855/https://books.google.ca/books?id=vT9YAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA687|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女性發生率較男性為高<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/Index.aspx|title=Sinusitis|accessdate=6 April 2015|date=April 3, 2012|publisher=U.S. National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404185948/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/sinusitis/Pages/Index.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-04}}</ref>。慢性鼻竇炎發生率約為12.5%<ref name="Ham2011">{{cite journal|title=Chronic rhinosinusitis: epidemiology and medical management|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-allergy-and-clinical-immunology_2011-10_128_4/page/693|author=Hamilos DL|date=October 2011|journal=The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.jaci.2011.08.004|volume=128|pages=693–707; quiz 708–9|pmid=21890184}}</ref>。美國花費於鼻竇炎治療上的金錢約達110億美金<ref name="Ros2015" />。鼻竇炎的無效治療相當氾濫，包含以抗細菌藥治療病毒性鼻竇炎<ref name="Ros2015" />。{{TOC limit|3}}

== 流行病學 ==
鼻竇炎是常見的病症，美國每年約有二千至三千萬人出現鼻竇炎的症狀<ref name=Review2010>{{cite journal | author = Anon JB | title = Upper respiratory infections | journal = Am. J. Med. | volume = 123 | issue = 4 Suppl | pages = S16–25 | date = April 2010 | pmid = 20350632 | doi = 10.1016/j.amjmed.2010.02.003 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Dykewicz MS, Hamilos DL | title = Rhinitis and sinusitis | journal = The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology | volume = 125 | issue = 2 Suppl 2 | pages = S103–15 | date = February 2010 | pmid = 20176255 | doi = 10.1016/j.jaci.2009.12.989 }}</ref>。約有12.5%的人會受到慢性鼻竇炎的影響<ref name=Ham2011/>。

== 研究 ==
近期的研究指出[[真菌|真菌]]可能和慢性鼻竇炎的形成有關，已在試驗中用過抗真菌製劑的治療方式，有混合性的效果<ref name="Leung2008">{{cite journal |vauthors=Leung RS, Katial R | title = The diagnosis and management of acute and chronic sinusitis | journal = Primary care | volume = 35 | issue = 1 | pages = 11–24, v–vi | date = March 2008 | pmid = 18206715 | doi = 10.1016/j.pop.2007.09.002 }}</ref>。

